'''罌粟麵包卷'''（'''poppy seed roll'''）是一種在[[中歐|中歐]]和[[東歐|東歐]]地區流行的食物，主要在[[聖誕節|聖誕節]]和[[復活節|復活節]]期間食用。罌粟麵包卷的做法是在麵包卷中填入[[罌粟|罌粟]]的種子和切碎的核桃糊<ref name="Dorcas">{{cite book|title=Hungarian recipes|editor=Dorcas Guild of the Magyar United Church of Christ|location=Elyria, Ohio|year=1960|pages=44}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.konyhamester.hu/index.php?frameaddress=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.konyhamester.hu%2Fa_r_t%2Frecept%2F295.htm |title=Mákos bejgli |access-date=2022-03-25 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119214456/http://www.konyhamester.hu/index.php?frameaddress=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.konyhamester.hu%2Fa_r_t%2Frecept%2F295.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://cross-cooking.eu/hu/node/438 |title=Diós és Mákos bejgli with picture |accessdate=2015-12-27 |archive-date=2012-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402044336/http://cross-cooking.eu/hu/node/438 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]，聖誕節期間食用的糕點並不多，罌粟麵包卷是匈牙利具代表性的聖誕節甜點。

